shortDescription: {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} have been pushing into this region, so there are big bounties out on them. Take out as many as you can --- the more you drop, the bigger your payout. Warzones can be extremely long, come prepared for extended combat!
longDescription: This is a straight-up brawl and we're on our own for this one. Stay frosty, Commander.

contractObjectiveList.title: Defeat all enemies and then some

dialogueContent.words: No backup is coming.  Employ all necessary measures to achieve the objectives: neutralize hostiles.
{TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym}'s forces are arriving to mop-up anyone left.  Hopefully you left some for them to play with.
Recon has spotted additional bogies coming your way.

Mission's done, Commander.  Any enemy units you take out from here on? That's bonus pay.  Feel free to stick around and clean up, but don't push your luck --- the {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} still has a strong presence in the area.  Head to the marked evac point when you're ready to pull out.
